      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $ABC$ un triangle de cotés $a,b,c$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(ABC\\)</span> un triangle de cotés <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a,b,c\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a0afec4b-2e1f-4629-959c-cb9069181e56",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer l'aire, $S$, de $ABC$ en fonction de $a,b,c$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer l’aire, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(S\\)</span>, de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(ABC\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a,b,c\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "86e7f5ce-2182-4346-bd7e-bd1d6c64f9cd",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$4S=\\sqrt{2a^2b^2 + 2a^2c^2 + 2b^2c^2 - a^4 - b^4 - c^4}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(4S=\\sqrt{2a^2b^2 + 2a^2c^2 + 2b^2c^2 - a^4 - b^4 - c^4}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ae26f27e-ff97-4a93-a08e-d6a36955c4cf",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $\\frac{S}{a^2+b^2+c^2}$ est maximal lorsque $ABC$ est équilatéral.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{S}{a^2+b^2+c^2}\\)</span> est maximal lorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(ABC\\)</span> est équilatéral.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6755e07a-b858-4d0a-83f6-9bc5b878334e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "max = $\\frac4{\\sqrt3}$.",
        "html": "<p>max = <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac4{\\sqrt3}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
